			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Go to the Colony Barracks using the debugbook\r\n- Engage Krustine and her Skull Lashers in combat\r\n- Magthew Budj will say this AD when he gets the chance. Each Myrkulite here will get the chance to say their own AD in each combat round (after everyone has had a turn). They will only be able to play this AD once."
				},
